Output demo.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set MarginFill "#181825"
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "presage chat"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 4s
Type "How does the geodesic trajectory predictor work?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 10s
Type "why does verify_token throw an AttributeError?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 10s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 2s
